2026-05-09T05:07:54.1125220Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-09T05:07:54.1125887Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-09T05:07:54.1126730Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-09T05:07:54.1127586Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-09T05:07:54.1128411Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-09T05:07:54.1129253Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-09T05:07:54.1130101Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-09T05:07:54.1130949Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
